		================================
		avfltctl - AVFlt Control Utility
			     README
		================================

1. Introduction

	AVFlt Control Utility allows to manage AVFlt registered to RedirFS from
	command line. This is preferred way how to manage AVFlt, but the AVFlt
	sysfs interface can be used directly also.

	For an overview of the RedirFS project, visit 

		http://www.redirfs.org

2. Installation

	See the INSTALL file.

3. Documentation

	http://www.redirfs.org/tiki-index.php?page=redirfs_doc

4. Problems & Bugs
	
	http://www.redirfs.org/cgi-bin/bugzilla/index.cgi
